### Icon Sizing

```css
/* Small icons (buttons, badges) */
width: 16px; height: 16px;

/* Default icons (navigation, actions) */
width: 18px; height: 18px;

/* Medium icons (cards, features) */
width: 20px; height: 20px;

/* Large icons (empty states, features) */
