## 7. Modal Pattern

```css
.modal-overlay {
  position: fixed;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  z-index: 1000;
}

.modal {
  background: white;
  border-radius: 12px;
  width: 640px;
  max-height: 90vh;
}

.modal-header { padding: 20px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
.modal-body { padding: 24px; max-height: 60vh; overflow-y: auto; }
.modal-footer { padding: 16px 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
```

